 market, he examines the pressing questions that philanthropy must tackle if it is to be equal to the challenges of the 21st century.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aCharities. 0aCharity organization. 0aSocial service. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Philanthropy & Charity.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBristol UP/Policy Press Complete eBook-Package 2023z97831111967940 cprintz978152922692840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781529226942423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781529226942/original  a978-3-11-119679-4  Bristol UP/Policy Press Complete eBook-Package 2023b2023  aGBV-deGruyter-alles